<sent type="title" lang="chi" page="01a" n="1">大學栗谷先生諺解</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="2">大學之道 在明明德며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="2">大學의 道 明德을 明호매 이시며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="3">在親民며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="3">民을 新호매 이시며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="4">在止於至善이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="4">至善의 止호매 잇니라</sent>
<sent type="anno" lang="chi" page="01a" n="5">親當作新</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="1">知止而后有定이니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="1">止 안 后애 定호미 이실디니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="2">定而后能靜고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="2">定 后애 能히 靜고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="3">靜而后能安고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="3">靜 后애 能히 安고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="4">安而后能慮고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="4">安 后애 能히 慮고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="5">慮而后能得이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="5">慮 后애 能히 得디니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="6">物有本末고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="6">物이 本과 末이 잇고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b-02a" n="7">事有終始니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b-02a" n="7">事ᅵ 終과 始ᅵ 이시니</sent><!--終^과-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="1">知所先後ᅵ면 則近道矣리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="1">몬져 며 후에  바 알면 道의 갓가오리라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="1">古之欲明明德於天下者 先治其國고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="1">녜 明德을 天下의 明코져  者 몬져 그 國을 治고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="2">欲治其國者 先齊其家고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="2">그 國을 治코져  者 몬져 그 家 齊고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="3">欲齊其家者 先脩其身고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="3">그 家 齊코져  者 몬져 그 身을 脩고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="4">欲脩其身者 先正其心고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="4">그 身을 脩코져  者 몬져 그 心을 正고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="5">欲正奇心者 先誠其意고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="5">그 心을 正코져  者 몬져 그 意 誠고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b-03a" n="6">欲誠其意者 先致其知니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b-03a" n="6">그 意 誠코져  者 몬져 그 知 致니</sent><!--^니-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="1">致知 在格物이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="1">知 致호 物을 格호매 잇니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="2">物格而后知至고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="2">物이 格 后애 知ᅵ 至고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="3">知至而后意誠고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="3">知ᅵ 至 后애 意ᅵ 誠고</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="1">意誠而后心正고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="1">意ᅵ 誠 后애 心이 正고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="2">心正而后身脩고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="2">心ᅵ 正 后애 身이 脩고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="3">身脩而后家齊고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="3">身ᅵ 脩 后애 家이 齊고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="4">家齊而后國治고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="4">家ᅵ 齊 后애 國이 治고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="5">國治而后天下平이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="5">國ᅵ 治 后애 天下이 平디니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="6">自天子以至於庶人히</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="6">天子로브터  庶人의 니르히</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="1">臺是皆以脩身為本이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="1">티 다 身을 脩호로  本을 사디니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="2">其本亂而末治者ᅵ 否矣며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="2">그 本이 亂코 末이 治 者ᅵ 업스며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="3">其所厚者薄이오 而其所薄者厚ᅵ 未之有也ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="3">그 厚 바의 薄고 그 薄 바의 厚리 잇디 아니니라</sent>
<sent type="title2" lang="chi" page="04a" n="4">右經 一章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="1">康誥曰 克明德이라 고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="1">康誥의 오 德을 克히 明다 고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="2">大甲曰 顧諟天之明命이라 고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="2">太甲의 오 이 天의 明 命을 顧다 고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="3">帝典曰 克明峻德이라 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="3">帝典의 오 峻 德을 克히 明다 니</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="1">皆自明也ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="1">다 스스로 明호미니라</sent>
<sent type="title2" lang="chi" page="05a" n="2">右傳之首章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="3">湯之盤銘曰</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="3">湯ᄉ 盤銘의 오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="4">茍日新이어든 日日新며 又日新이라 고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="4">진실로 날애 新거든 나날 新며  날로 新라 고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a-05b" n="5">康誥曰 作新民이라 고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a-05b" n="5">康誥의 오 新 民을 作라 고</sent><!--作^-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="1">詩曰 周雖舊邦이나 其命維新이라 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="1">詩예 오 周ᅵ 비록 녯 나라히나 그 命이 新다 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="2">是故君子 無所不用其極이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="2">이런 故로 君子 그 極을 디 아닐 배 업스니라</sent>
<sent type="title2" lang="chi" page="05b" n="3">右傳之二章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="1">詩云 邦畿千里여 惟民所止라 도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="1">詩예 닐오 邦읫 畿ᅵ 千里여 民의 止 배라 도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="2">詩云 緡蠻黃鳥ᅵ 止于丘隅ᅵ라 야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="2">詩예 닐오 緡蠻 黃鳥ᅵ 丘隅에 止타 야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a-06b" n="3">子曰 於止예 知其所止로소니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a-06b" n="3">子ᅵ 샤 止 제 그 止 바 아노소니</sent><!--^-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="1">可以人而不如鳥乎아 시니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="1">可히 人으로  鳥만 디 몯 것가 시니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b-07a" n="2">詩云 穆穆文王이여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b-07a" n="2">詩예 닐오 穆穆신 文王이여</sent><!--王^이-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="1">於緝熙敬止라 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="1">於홉다 니워 熙야 敬고 止시다 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="2">為人君얀 止於仁시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="2">人君이 되얀 仁의 止시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="3">為人臣얀 止於敬시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="3">人臣이 되얀 敬의 止시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="4">為人子얀 止於孝시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="4">人子ᅵ 되얀 孝의 止시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="5">為人父얀 止於慈시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="5">人父ᅵ 되얀 慈의 止시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="6">與國人交앤 止於信이러시다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="6">國人과 더브러 交호매 信에 止더시다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="1">詩云 瞻彼淇澳혼</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="1">詩예 닐오 뎌 淇澳을 본</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="2">菉竹猗猗로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="2">菉 竹이 猗猗도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="3">有斐君子ᅵ여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="3">斐 君子ᅵ여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="4">如切如磋며 如琢如磨ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="4">切 며 磋 며 琢 며 磨 도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="5">瑟兮僩兮며 赫兮喧兮라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="5">瑟며 僩며 赫며 喧디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="6">有斐君子ᅵ여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="6">斐 君子ᅵ여</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="7">終不可諠兮로다 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="7">내 可히 닛디 몯리로다 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="8">如切如磋者 道學也ᅵ오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="8">切 磋 호 學을 닐오미오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="9">如琢如磨者 自脩也ᅵ오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="9">琢 磨 호 스스로 脩호미오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="10">瑟兮僩兮者 恂慄也ᅵ오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="10">瑟며 僩호 恂慄호미오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="11">赫兮喧兮者 威儀也ᅵ오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="11">赫며 喧호믄 威儀오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a-08b" n="12">有斐君子終不可諠兮者 道盛德至善을 民之不能忘也ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a-08b" n="12">斐 君子 내 可히 닛디 몯호믄 盛 德과 지극 善을 民이 能히 닛디 몯호 니니라</sent><!-- ^ 君-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="1">詩云 於戲前王不忘이라 나</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="1">詩예 닐오 於戱ᅵ라 前王을 닛디 몯리로다 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b-09a" n="2">君子 賢其賢而親其親고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b-09a" n="2">君子 그 賢샤 賢히 너기며 그 親샤 親히 너기시고</sent><!--그 ^ 賢-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="1">小人은 樂其樂而利其利라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="1">小人은 그 樂게 샤 樂히 너기며 그 利케 샤 利히 너기디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="2">此以沒世不忘也ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="2">이  世沒호 닛디 몯호미니라</sent>
<sent type="title2" lang="chi" page="09a" n="3">右傳之三章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="1">子曰 聽訟이 吾猶人也ᅵ나</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="1">子ᅵ 샤 訟을 聽기 내 人 나</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="2">必也使無訟乎뎌 시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="2">반시 여곰 訟을 업게 딘뎌 시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="3">無情者ᅵ 不得盡其辭 大畏民志니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="3">情 업슨 者ᅵ 시러곰 그 辭 盡티 몯호 크게 民의 志를 畏케 호미니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="4">此謂知本이니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09b" n="4">이 닐온 本을 알오미니라</sent>
<sent type="title2" lang="chi" page="09b" n="5">右傳之四章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09b" n="6">此謂知本</sent><!--구결도 없고 언해문도 없음-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="10a" n="1">此謂知之至也ᅵ니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="10a" n="1">이 닐온 知의 至호미니라</sent>
<sent type="title2" lang="chi" page="10a" n="2">右傳之五章</sent>

<sent type="main2" lang="chi" page="10b" n="1">間嘗竊取程子之意以補之니</sent><!--상단에 “此章栗谷先生吐釋缺”이라고 적혀 있음-->
<sent type="main2" lang="kor" page="10b" n="1">근간의 일즉 程子 을 竊取야  補니</sent>
<sent type="main2" lang="chi" page="10b" n="2">曰所謂致知在格物者</sent>
